	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You empty a flask containing a bit of tallow, a pinch of brimstone, and a dusting of powdered iron on the ground. As you say a few magic words in a firm voice, you create a flaming confluence of elemental energy.</em></p><p><strong>Summoning Spell</strong></p><p>You create an sphere of fire.</p><ul><li><p>It is a medium &amp;reference[elemental]{elemental} and acts immediately after the end of your turn.</p></li><li><p>It is immune to &amp;reference[fire]{fire} and &amp;reference[poison]{poison} damage, and immune to the &amp;reference[grappled]{grappled}, &amp;reference[paralyzed]{paralyzed}, &amp;reference[petrified]{petrified}, &amp;reference[poisoned]{poisoned}, &amp;reference[prone]{prone}, &amp;reference[restrained]{restrained}, &amp;reference[unconscious], and &amp;reference[exhaustion]{exhaustion} conditions.</p></li><li><p>It has AC 10, 20 hit points,* and all its ability scores are 2, except &amp;reference[dexterity]{dexterity} and &amp;reference[constitution]{constitution} which are 10.</p></li><li><p>Its speed is 30 and can move through other creatures (but not end in their space).</p></li><li><p>It emits &amp;reference[brightlight] in a 20 ft. radius and &amp;reference[dimlight] in a 40 ft. radius.</p></li><li><p>At the end of each of the sphere's turns or if the sphere is reduced to 0 hit points, any creature within 5 feet of the sphere makes a dexterity save.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6 fire]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> The sphere's hit points increase by 10 and its damage increases by [[/r 1d6 fire]]{1d6} for each spell level above 2nd level.</p>",
